{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1147,"text":"I want to talk to you today"},{"time":3110,"text":"about a difficult topic\nthat is close to me,"},{"time":6397,"text":"and closer than you might realize to you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":11053,"text":"I came to the UK 21 years ago,\nas an asylum-seeker."},{"time":17046,"text":"I was 21."},{"time":18950,"text":"I was forced to leave\nthe Democratic Republic of the Congo,"},{"time":22829,"text":"my home, where I was a student activist."},{"time":28836,"text":"I would love my children to be able\nto meet my family in the Congo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36095,"text":"But I want to tell you\nwhat the Congo has got to do with you."},{"time":41221,"text":"But first of all,\nI want you to do me a favor."},{"time":45289,"text":"Can you all please reach into your pockets\nand take out your mobile phone?"},{"time":53819,"text":"Feel that familiar weight ..."},{"time":58423,"text":"how naturally your finger\nslides towards the buttons."}]},{"cues":[{"time":61614,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":64814,"text":"Can you imagine your world without it?"},{"time":67017,"text":"It connects us to our loved ones,"},{"time":69525,"text":"our family, friends and colleagues,"},{"time":73168,"text":"at home and overseas."},{"time":75785,"text":"It is a symbol of an interconnected world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80358,"text":"But what you hold in your hand\nleaves a bloody trail,"},{"time":86204,"text":"and it all boils down to a mineral:"},{"time":90089,"text":"tantalum, mined in the Congo as coltan."},{"time":94416,"text":"It is an anticorrosive heat conductor."},{"time":97916,"text":"It stores energy in our mobile phones,\nPlayStations and laptops."},{"time":104816,"text":"It is used in aerospace\nand medical equipment as an alloy."},{"time":111110,"text":"It is so powerful\nthat we only need tiny amounts."},{"time":116343,"text":"It would be great\nif the story ended there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120209,"text":"Unfortunately, what you hold in your hand"},{"time":123887,"text":"has not only enabled incredible\ntechnological development"},{"time":129624,"text":"and industrial expansion,"},{"time":132481,"text":"but it has also contributed\nto unimaginable human suffering."}]},{"cues":[{"time":138088,"text":"Since 1996,"},{"time":140819,"text":"over five million people have died\nin the Democratic Republic of the Congo."},{"time":147038,"text":"Countless women, men and children\nhave been raped, tortured or enslaved."},{"time":155076,"text":"Rape is used as a weapon of war,"},{"time":157903,"text":"instilling fear\nand depopulating whole areas."},{"time":163379,"text":"The quest for extracting this mineral"},{"time":167350,"text":"has not only aided, but it has fueled"},{"time":172033,"text":"the ongoing war in the Congo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177275,"text":"But don't throw away your phones yet."},{"time":180669,"text":"Thirty thousand children are enlisted"},{"time":184779,"text":"and are made to fight in armed groups."},{"time":190158,"text":"The Congo consistently scores dreadfully"},{"time":194139,"text":"in global health and poverty rankings."},{"time":198667,"text":"But remarkably,"},{"time":200144,"text":"the UN Environmental Programme\nhas estimated the wealth of the country"},{"time":205864,"text":"to be over 24 trillion dollars."},{"time":216026,"text":"The state-regulated mining\nindustry has collapsed,"},{"time":219909,"text":"and control over mines has splintered."},{"time":223598,"text":"Coltan is easily controlled\nby armed groups."},{"time":228046,"text":"One well-known illicit trade route\nis that across the border to Rwanda,"},{"time":233254,"text":"where Congolese tantalum\nis disguised as Rwandan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":238211,"text":"But don't throw away your phones yet,"},{"time":240881,"text":"because the incredible irony"},{"time":243738,"text":"is that the technology\nthat has placed such unsustainable,"},{"time":247106,"text":"devastating demands on the Congo"},{"time":250135,"text":"is the same technology that has brought\nthis situation to our attention."},{"time":256801,"text":"We only know so much about the situation\nin the Congo and in the mines"},{"time":261745,"text":"because of the kind of communication\nthe mobile phone allows."},{"time":268225,"text":"As with the Arab Spring,"},{"time":270527,"text":"during the recent elections in the Congo,"},{"time":273888,"text":"voters were able to send text messages\nof local polling stations"},{"time":279961,"text":"to the headquarters\nin the capital, Kinshasa."},{"time":284673,"text":"And in the wake of the result,"},{"time":290027,"text":"the diaspora has joined\nwith the Carter Center,"},{"time":293748,"text":"the Catholic Church and other observers,"},{"time":297129,"text":"to draw attention\nto the undemocratic result."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302232,"text":"The mobile phone has given\npeople around the world"},{"time":307671,"text":"an important tool towards gaining\ntheir political freedom."},{"time":312965,"text":"It has truly revolutionized the way\nwe communicate on the planet."},{"time":318856,"text":"It has allowed momentous\npolitical change to take place."},{"time":324572,"text":"So, we are faced with a paradox."},{"time":330503,"text":"The mobile phone\nis an instrument of freedom"},{"time":334570,"text":"and an instrument of oppression."}]},{"cues":[{"time":340015,"text":"TED has always celebrated\nwhat technology can do for us,"},{"time":346410,"text":"technology in its finished form."},{"time":348965,"text":"It is time to be asking questions\nabout technology."},{"time":354831,"text":"Where does it come from?"},{"time":357164,"text":"Who makes it?"},{"time":359815,"text":"And for what?"},{"time":362578,"text":"Here, I am speaking directly to you,"},{"time":366006,"text":"the TED community,"},{"time":367769,"text":"and to all those who might\nbe watching on a screen,"},{"time":371585,"text":"on your phone, across the world,"},{"time":374962,"text":"in the Congo."},{"time":377477,"text":"All the technology is in place\nfor us to communicate,"},{"time":381771,"text":"and all the technology is in place\nto communicate this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":388759,"text":"At the moment,"},{"time":390659,"text":"there is no clear fair-trade solution."},{"time":395287,"text":"But there has been\na huge amount of progress."},{"time":398667,"text":"The US has recently passed legislation"},{"time":402319,"text":"to target bribery\nand misconduct in the Congo."},{"time":406167,"text":"Recent UK legislation\ncould be used in the same way."},{"time":411726,"text":"In February, Nokia unveiled its new policy\non sourcing minerals in the Congo,"},{"time":418005,"text":"and there is a petition to Apple\nto make a conflict-free iPhone."},{"time":426492,"text":"There are campaigns spreading\nacross university campuses"},{"time":430877,"text":"to make their colleges conflict-free."},{"time":434335,"text":"But we're not there yet."},{"time":436493,"text":"We need to continue\nmounting pressure on phone companies"},{"time":442536,"text":"to change their sourcing processes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":446506,"text":"When I first came to the UK, 21 years ago,"},{"time":450274,"text":"I was homesick."},{"time":452643,"text":"I missed my family\nand the friends I left behind."},{"time":457845,"text":"Communication was extremely difficult."},{"time":461467,"text":"Sending and receiving\nletters took months --"},{"time":465195,"text":"if you were lucky."},{"time":466725,"text":"Often, they never arrived."},{"time":470172,"text":"Even if I could have afforded\nthe phone bills home,"},{"time":475539,"text":"like most people in the Congo,"},{"time":477955,"text":"my parents did not own a phone line."}]},{"cues":[{"time":481986,"text":"Today, my two sons --"},{"time":488408,"text":"David and Daniel,"},{"time":490486,"text":"can talk to my parents\nand get to know them."},{"time":497917,"text":"Why should we allow"},{"time":500727,"text":"such a wonderful, brilliant\nand necessary product"},{"time":507646,"text":"to be the cause of unnecessary suffering"},{"time":511605,"text":"for human beings?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":514732,"text":"We demand fair-trade food\nand fair-trade clothes."},{"time":519632,"text":"It is time to demand fair-trade phones."},{"time":524458,"text":"This is an idea worth spreading."}]},{"cues":[{"time":527853,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":529035,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}